We shall know soon, better than seers could tell us.
—My son, hearing the fixed doom of thy betrothed, art thou come in rage against thy father? Or have I thy good-will, act how I may ?Hœ.
Father, I am thine;
and thou, in thy wisdom, tracest for me rules which I shall follow.
